{"tid":1992210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"棄任主席捱批 梁耀忠：主席較少發言機會 真係唔想做","createTime":"2020-04-28T04:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T08:14:04.000Z","uid":113222,"like":76,"dislike":593,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe4be326cab6f586977d2d6f7469e33cb4434f6","tid":1992210,"uid":113222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T04:24:00.000Z","msg":"立法會根據《建造業議會條例》及《肺塵埃沉着病及間皮瘤（補償）條例》提出的擬議決議案小組委員會，在6月6日開會選舉委員會主席。<span style=\"color: red;\">梁耀忠因為議員資歷排名第一，獲機會主持會議。</span>當時會議室內僅有民建聯黃定光和勞聯潘兆平，黃定光欲提名梁耀忠擔任主席，<span style=\"color: red;\">梁耀忠稱：「唔好呀！千祈唔好呀！你知我最唔鍾意做呢樣嘢㗎啦，千祈唔好！」梁耀忠反建議黃定光及潘兆平擔任</span>，三人互相推搪，最後由工聯會何啟明擔任主席。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1057901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1057901&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=6cb85479\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1057901&h=f6222679\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1057901</a><br />\n<br />\n面對中共DQ壓境，泛民唔知會唔會又跪共求存。<br />\n<br />\n但前線示威已經流左好多血，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">鄭重警告：如果泛民再賣港，唔會再有香港人投你地！你地一樣無得生存！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e05bfb0f60548a54dd7aac1cb366738f41033150","tid":1992210,"uid":113222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T04:26:04.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"716cbeff84270ef5d5322ed14cd4e58850c2acc3","tid":1992210,"uid":55597,"like":199,"dislike":2,"score":197,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T04:26:15.000Z","msg":"你係代議士<br />\n做唔做，用個人情感決定？"},{"pid":"7ad2647a9b872d2f133e737cf8bd5386e2ac1699","tid":1992210,"uid":14494,"like":118,"dislike":2,"score":116,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T04:27:22.000Z","msg":"雖然old news, 但比d壓力白頭佬就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9e89eb3fc15ffc45fcbe6a7ff10e4e839270e7","tid":1992210,"uid":112581,"like":86,"dislike":0